 nam nhi) - 遣興（驥子好男兒）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Thi%C3%AAn-M%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-zL1WjWsx954wTVcqqmOLTA">Tặng Thiên Mụ tự hoà thượng - 贈天姥寺和尚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-tVCgetl94ylIpxXT-wJP2g">Phan Quế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-T%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%C3%AAn/T%C3%B2ng-gi%C3%A1-h%E1%BA%A1nh-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C3%A2m-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-ZyrwxrlmYbFaBPuORlM3UQ">Tòng giá hạnh Thiếu Lâm tự - 從駕幸少林寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-T%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%C3%AAn/author-cFPknskEldD7UcWhT6LIfQ">Võ Tắc Thiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/T%E1%BB%A9-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-nh%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-IhPnTObeMROQAlriknY96g">Tứ nguyệt thập ngũ nhật cảm tác - 四月十五日感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/%E1%BB%A8c-Trung-d%C5%A9ng-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4n-%C4%90%C3%A0i-h%E1%BB%93i-thi-tr%C3%ACnh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-PqSwvT4-WTN5Y1giD7HeKg">Ức Trung dũng Thiếu phó Đặng Tôn Đài, hồi thi trình thướng kỳ 2 - 憶中勇少傅鄧尊台，回詩呈上其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
